al" hreflang="en">Mayor Nathan Pachal</a></h3></div><div class="views-field views-field-field-email"><strong class="views-label views-label-field-email">Email: </strong><span class="field-content"><a href="mailto:npachal@langleycity.ca">npachal@langleycity.ca</a></span></div></div></span></div></div><div class="views-row"><div class="views-field views-field-field-image"><div class="field-content"> <img loading="lazy" src="/sites/default/files/styles/1_1/public/2024-11/7_0.png?itok=E_bSM_4e" width="440" height="440" typeof="foaf:Image" class="image-style-_-1" /></div></div><div class="views-field views-field-fieldset"><span class="field-content"><div ><div class="views-field views-field-title"><h3 class="field-content"><a href="/city-hall/city-council/councillor-paul-albrecht" hreflang="en">Councillor Paul Albrecht</a></h3></div><div class="views-field views-field-field-email"><strong class="views-label views-label-field-email">Email: </strong><span class="field-content"><a href="mailto:palbrecht@langleycity.ca">palbrecht@langleycity.ca</a></span></div><div class="views-field views-field-field-committees-and-appointment"><strong class="views-label views-label-field-committees-and-appointment">Committees and appointments: </strong><span class="field-content">Crime Prevention Committee, Environmental Sustainability Committee, Socio-Cultural and Economic Development Advisory Committee (SCEDAC)</span></div></div></span></div></div><div class="views-row"><div class="views-field views-field-field-image"><div class="field-content"> <img loading="lazy" src="/sites/default/files/styles/1_1/public/2024-11/2_0.png?itok=cpFX_3sx" width="440" height="440" typeof="foaf:Image" class="image-style-_-1" /></div></div><div class="views-field views-field-fieldset"><span class="field-content"><div ><div class="views-field views-field-title"><h3 class="field-content"><a href="/city-hall/city-council/councillor-delaney-mack" hreflang="en">Councillor Delaney Mack</a></h3></div><div class="v